{"tid":2277353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國示威 水炮車再次出水","createTime":"2020-11-08T11:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T12:55:46.000Z","uid":169262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bd59f30e9fd8d96cb7f656862c3c6ae41db55aa8","tid":2277353,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T11:54:03.000Z","msg":"剛剛有一點混亂，有用水炮車噴水<br />\n7<br />\n但沒有誰很嚴重受傷，我來不及看，記者們也都來不及，但救護車到場了<br />\n<br />\n現在已經把人推出危險線了，大家已經坐下了<br />\n警察和示威已經隔開了，雙方都控制得很好，警察有對示威們道歉了。<br />\n<br />\n今天警察們沒有帶棍子，如果沒什麼失控情況應該安全。<br />\n<br />\n現在示威已經靠近大皇宮了，為了遞信給國王。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/169194527226035/posts/834543840691097/?sfnsn=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F169194527226035%2Fposts%2F834543840691097%2F%3Fsfnsn%3Dmo&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq7%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=dba22450\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/169194527226035/posts/834543840691097/?sfnsn=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/115562146559518/posts/386855036096893/?sfnsn=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F115562146559518%2Fposts%2F386855036096893%2F%3Fsfnsn%3Dmo&d=TOASGvm2FfjCvYiV2fDq7%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=4d6bcb9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/115562146559518/posts/386855036096893/?sfnsn=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ffGNndN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FffGNndN.jpg&h=bdc42de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QpKZXM8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQpKZXM8.jpg&h=5d981ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sn3LTku.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsn3LTku.jpg&h=02393dcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3hXKsa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn